{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become Your Worst Nightmare's Worst Nightmare</h2><br>Live the dream! Dash, hack, slash, and yo-yo your way through this deceptively charming, devilishly challenging roguelike bullet-hell. Carve through baddies and bosses with dozens of unique abilities. Collect and stack items to augment your stats and enhance your skills, and unlock an excessive cast of playable characters.<br><br>In this game, you can:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>slap enemies with a fish<br></li><li>create a storm to throw pies at your foes<br></li><li>weaponize a laser pointer<br></li><li>summon an army of bees<br></li><li>break some eggs<br></li><li>command an armada of space stations<br></li><li>blow bubbles<br></li><li>howl at the moon<br></li><li>...and much more!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512680/extras/3chargift.gif?t=1723229571\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Just a Quick Nap</h2><br>Featuring runs shorter than 30 minutes, enjoy wild builds and zero-to-hero roguelike catharsis in a fraction of the time. Light meta-progression ensures you will find the game beatable from your very first run.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Broken Dreams</h2><br>Collect and stack dozens of items, from beehives and balloons, to scarecrows and swords. Choose upgrades to modify your abilities and stats as you craft outrageously broken builds.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512680/extras/desert_knife_gif.gif?t=1723229571\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You, Who?</h2><br>From an angler with a fishing hook to a clown with juggling clubs, unlock and master more than 20 playable characters, each with different stats and abilities. If you enjoy discovering new ways to play, there's plenty to wrap your mind around here.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512680/extras/unlock_angler_